Interface CachedNetworkIO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NetworkIO
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CachedNetworkIOWM

    public interface CachedNetworkIO
extends NetworkIO
    This interface defines methods related to cached network input and output.
